{"tid":2044199,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《銀河守護隊》導演James Gunn自爆係港產片狂迷：邱淑貞係我女神","createTime":"2020-05-31T03:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T14:46:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8713643585bc62d16f0d6c8159c096d3521f13ed","tid":2044199,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"荷里活導演James Gunn因執導《銀河守護隊》（Guardians of the Galaxy）和《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》（The Suicide Squad）等多套Marvel電影而聲名大噪。近日這位名導就參加了一個「30天電影挑戰」（30 Days Challenge），連續30日分享電影的題材。<br />\n<br />\n來到第16天的題目「A Film that is personal to you」（對自己最有意義的電影），他竟然揀選了一套1992年上映，由邱淑貞和任達華主演的香港三級電影《赤裸羔羊》。<br />\n<br />\n帖文中，James Gunn就講到，自從1992年在紐約一間戲院看過《赤裸羔羊》之後，就愛上了香港電影：「霍耀良執導的電影中的血腥、動作、性元素震撼了我。邱淑貞變成了我的女神，而任達華就成為了我想變成的人。」他特別提到，當其時美國還不是十分流行香港電影，所以他花了很多時間在當地尋找香港電影的錄影帶（VHS），最終也在兩年之內收藏了超過100套的香港電影的錄影帶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200530/343499821107253248.jpeg/71cIKv6-LyeczgQqiz2Bmxzj70KwZBCL3Y1XNt2NVzY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200530%2F343499821107253248.jpeg%2F71cIKv6-LyeczgQqiz2Bmxzj70KwZBCL3Y1XNt2NVzY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dc4a58fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200530/343493845272629248.jpeg/4kG8ItSvlSRjR8tkoBjABMxny1Txajzx79hM0u_YTNI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200530%2F343493845272629248.jpeg%2F4kG8ItSvlSRjR8tkoBjABMxny1Txajzx79hM0u_YTNI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8efb6e61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df8946aebfc3cccd3cf96378b1ef51fd15541e7e","tid":2044199,"uid":39710,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"8713643585bc62d16f0d6c8159c096d3521f13ed","tid":2044199,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"荷里活導演James Gunn因執導《銀河守護隊》（Guardians of the Galaxy）和《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》（The Suicide Squad）等多套Marvel電影而聲名大噪。近日這位名導就參加了一個「30天電影挑戰」（30 Da